  52,25,"Yoga ma…ì…ìe fewtita yoga, …ìe lamndondira"
  52,26,"…ìe wi'a: \"Pellet, men laatino ado [hannde], hulunoo…ìe [lepte …óen] hakkunde yim…ìe amen"
  52,27,"Allah mo∆¥∆¥ii e amen, O da…óni men lepte Norngal"
  52,28,"Men laatino ado [hannde], torotonoo…ìe Mo. Pellet, ko Kanko woni Mo∆¥∆¥o, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  52,29,"Anndintin tun, sabu neema Joomi maa on, a wonaa ndureejo wanaa a feetu…óo"
