  52,38,Kaa …ìe jogiti …ìargal ngal …ìe jentorta? Awa yo he…óitii…óo ma…ì…ìe on addu hujja …ìanngu…óo
  52,39,"Kaa hara ko …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe woodanta Mo, onon kan wor…ìe …ìen"
  52,40,"Kaa a lamndi …ìe njo…ìdi, hara yo…ìugol ndi no teddani …ìe"
  52,41,"Kaa …ìe anndu fii wirnii…ói …óin, hara hi…ìe winnda"
  52,42,"Kaa …ìe faala fewjoore? Doo ko yeddu…ìe …ìen, woni fooletee…ìe pewje …ìen"
  52,43,"Kaa hi…ìe mari rewetee…óo ko woori Allah? Senaade woodanii Allah, e kon ko …ìe sirkata"
  52,44,"Si …ìe yi'ii ta∆¥atine immornde ka kammu no yani, …ìe wi'a: \"Ko duule fawondir…óe"
  52,45,"Terto …ìe, haa …ìe hawroya e √±alaande ma…ì…ìe nde …ìe leptoytee e mun"
  52,46,"√ëalnde nde pewje ma…ì…ìe duncanoytaa …ìe hay huunde, …ìe wonaa kadi walloytee…ìe"
  52,47,"Ko pellet, hino woodani too√±u…ìe …ìen, lepte goo ko wanaa …óen …óon. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude kon e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe anndaa"
  52,48,"Mu√±√±o √±aawoore Joomi maa nden. Tawde pellet, hi…óa e ndenka Amen. Seniniraa yettugol Joomi maa, tuma …ìa≈ãoto…óaa"
