  57,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi seninii Allah. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±o On"
  57,2,"Ko Kanko heeranii laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Himo wuurna Himo wara, Kanko ko O hattan…óo kala huunde"
  57,3,"Ko Kanko woni Arano e Sakkitii…óo, Fee√±u…óo e Wirnii…óo, Kanko ko O anndu…óo kala huunde"
  57,4,"Ko Kanko tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin nder bal…óe jeegoo, refti O fotondiri ka dow \"Arsi\"; Himo anndi ko mutata kon ka leydi, e ko ∆¥awata e mayri, e ko jipporta ka kammu e ko ∆¥awata e maggu. Himo wonndi e mon kala ka won…óon. Allah no reeni ko golloton kon. @Corrected"
  57,5,Ko Kanko heeranii laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Ko ka Allah fiyakuuji …óin ruttirtee
  57,6,"Himo naadia jemma on e nder √±alorma on, O naadira √±alorma on kadi e nder jemma on. Kanko ko O anndu…óo ko woni e nder …ìer…óe"
  57,7,"Gom…óinee Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, nafqon kon ko O wa…óiri on lomtinaa…ìe e mun. Gom…óim…ìe …ìen e mon, …ìe nafqi [jawle ma…ì…ìe …óen], hino woodani …ìen njo…ìdi mawnundi"
  57,8,"E ko he…ìi on, on gom…óintaa Allah? E hino Nulaa…óo on hino nodda on e gom…óingol Joomi mon. Gom…óii [Allah] ∆¥ettii e mon ahadi, si on laatike gom…óim…ìe"
  57,9,"Ko Kanko jippinta e jeyaa…óo Makko on Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe, fii no o yaltinira on e ni…ìe faade e ndaygu. Pellet, Allah ko Yuminoowo on, Hinnotoo…óo"
  57,10,"E ko he…ìi on, on sakkotaako fii laawol Allah ngol, e hino le ko Allah woodani ronugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin? Fotataa e mon, …ìen sakkinoo…ìe ado uddital ngal …ìe ha…ìidaa; ko …ìen …ìuri mawnude darja e dii …ìen sakkii…ìe …ìaawo …óum …ìe ha…ìidaa. ∆Åe fow ma…ì…ìe non, Allah fodii …ìe mo∆¥∆¥ere. Allah no humpitii ko golloton kon"
  57,11,"Ko hommbo √±awlirta Allah √±amaande labaande, O sowana mo nde, hara no woodani mo njo…ìdi teddundi"
  57,12,"√ëalnde yi'oytaa gom…óim…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe rew…ìe …ìen, hara annoora ma…ì…ìe yaara yeeso ma…ì…ìe e √±aamo ma…ì…ìe (…ìe wi'anee): \"Weltaare mon hannde ko Aljannaaji, …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley mun, ko on duumotoo…ìe nder ton\". Ko …óum woni malal mawngal ngal"
  57,13,"√ëalnde naafiqii…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e naafiqii…ìe rew…ìe …ìen wi'anoyta gom…óim…ìe …ìen: \"Habbee men, men jalbinora annoora mon on\". ∆Åe wi'anee : \"Yiltoree …ìaawo mon, …óa…ì…ìoyon annoora\". Heedo wa…óee hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, ngo damal ngal yurmeende woni e nder mun, …ìaawo maggal noon, ko lepte woni e bannge mun"
  57,14,"Hi…ìe nodda …ìe : \"E men wondaano e mon?\" ∆Åe wi'a : \"Ko non woniri. Ko woni tun, on fitinno ko'e mon, habbitani…óon [gom…óim…ìe …ìen bone], sikkiti…óon, yelaaji hodi on haa yamiroore Allah nden ari. Hodoowo on hodi on e mo∆¥∆¥ere Allah nden"
  57,15,"Hannde on, on ja…ìantaake soktor…óum wanaa e …ìen yeddu…ìe. Depporde mon nden ko ka Yiite : ko ngen woni ko hanndu…óon. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  57,16,"E yontaani gom…óim…ìe …ìen nde …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen dee∆¥irta jantoore Allah nden e kon ko jippii immorde e goonga? Hara …ìe wa'aali wa …ìen okkanoo…ìe Defte …ìen ko adii, dumunna on juutani …ìen, …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen yoori, ko …óuu…óunoo e ma…ì…ìe kon ko faasiqii…ìe"
  57,17,"Anndee pellet, Allah wuurnitay leydi ndin …ìaawo ndi yoorii. Gom…óii Men …ìannginiranii on Aayeeje …óen, fii no haqqiliron"
  57,18,"Pellet, sakkotoo…ìe (jawle mun …ìen) ka wor…ìe e ka rew…ìe …ìe √±awli Allah √±amaande labaande, …ìe sowanoyte (mbarjaari) hara no woodani …ìe njo…ìdi mawndi"
  57,19,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, ko …ìen woni goongiya≈ãke en. Sahodin…ìe …ìen ka Joomi mun, hino woodani …ìen njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe e annoora ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åen non yeddu…ìe …ìe fenni Aayeeje Amen …óen, ko …ìen woni yim…ìe Jahiimi ngen"
  57,20,"Anndee wonnde nguurndam aduna …óam ko fijindaaru, e mbelee…óe, e cu…óaari, e …ìurondiro hakkunde mon e jawle e …ìi…ó…ìe. Wano to…ìo haawnungo remoo…ìe …ìen pu…ói mun, refti ngo yoora, yi'aa hingo soy…ói; refti ngo wonta muncii…óum. Hino ka laakara, lette sa…ótu…óe, e yaafuyee immorde e Allah e yarluyee. Nguurndam aduna …óam wonaali, si wanaa dakammehoy hodo"
  57,21,"Adondiree e (golle) yaafaawuya ka Joomi mon, e Aljanna mo yaajeendi mun wa'i yaajeendi kammu ngun e leydi ndin, on maranaama …ìen gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen. ∆äum ko …ìural Allah ngal O okkata on mo O muuyani. Allah ko Jom …ìural mawnungal"
  57,22,"Bone woo he…ìataa [on] e leydi ndin maa e pittaali mon …óin, si wanaa …óum woniino e deftere ado Men tagude ndee [tagoore]. Pellet, …óum ko ko newanii Allah"
  57,23,"Ko fii wata on suno e ko laawii on kon, wanaa kadi weltorgol ko O okki on kon. Allah yi…óaa kala √±aa∆¥oowo, mantii…óo"
  57,24,"∆Åen wuddoo…ìe …ìe yamira yim…ìe …ìen nguddam... kala …óuurnii…óo, pellet, Allah kan ko Galo, Yettinii…óo"
  57,25,"Gom…óii Men nulirii Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen …ìanngannduyeeji, Men jippindinani …ìe Defte e sariyaare, fii no yim…ìe …ìen √±ii…ìira e nun…óal. Men jippini kadi njamndi ndin, ndi doole tii…óu…óe woni e mun e nafooje wonannde yim…ìe …ìen, e no Allah fe√±√±inira …ìen walloo…ìe Mo e Nulaa…óo Makko on ka wirnii. Pellet, Allah ko Jom cemmbe, Foolu…óo. @Corrected"
  57,26,"Gom…óii Men nulii Nuuhu e Ibraahiima, Men wa…ói e geyngol ma…ì…ìe ngol Annabaaku e Defte. Hino e ma…ì…ìe feewu…ìe, ko …óuu…ói kon e ma…ì…ìe ko faasiqii…ìe"
  57,27,"Refti Men jokkindini e batteeji ma…ì…ìe …óin, Nulaa…ìe Amen [goo], Men jokkintiniri […ìe] Iisaa ge…óal Maryama on, Men okki mo Linjiila, Men wa…ói e …ìer…óe jokku…ìe mo …ìen : yurmeende e giggol. Labbeyaagal ngal …ìe sinci ngal, Menen Men wa…ó…óinaa ngal e ma…ì…ìe. [Men lamndaaki] si wanaa …óa…ì…ìugol welayee Allah. Kono …ìe ayniraali …óum no haani aynireede. Men okki njo…ìdi gom…óim…ìe …ìen e ma…ì…ìe. Ko …óuu…óunoo kon e ma…ì…ìe ko faasiqii…ìe"
  57,28,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe! Hulee Allah, gom…óinon Nulaa…óo Makko on; O ye…óay on ge…óe …ói…ói e mbarjaari Makko ndin, O wa…óana on annoora mo ndayginorton, O haforana on. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  57,29,"Fii no yim…ìe Defte …ìen anndira wonnde …ìe hattanaa hay huunde e …ìural Allah ngal, e wonnde …ìural ngal ko e juu…óe Allah woni; Himo ye…óa ngal mo O muuyani. Pellet, Allah ko Jom …ìural mawngal"